@startuml MyCPT_Sequence_Chemistry

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Apple SD Gothic Neo, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam defaultFontColor #26215C
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #AFA9EC
  FontColor #26215C
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #7F77DD
  FontColor #3C3489
  FontSize 12
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #7F77DD
  ArrowFontColor #534AB7
  ArrowFontSize 10
  LifeLineBorderColor #AFA9EC
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  GroupBorderColor #534AB7
  GroupBackgroundColor #EEEDFE
  GroupFontColor #3C3489
  GroupFontSize 11
  GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  DividerBackgroundColor #EEEDFE
  DividerBorderColor #534AB7
  DividerFontColor #3C3489
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  BorderColor #AFA9EC
  FontColor #534AB7
  FontSize 10
}

actor "발행자 (회원 A)" as UserA
actor "구독자 (회원 C)\n동일 버킷 조합" as UserC
actor "상대방 (회원 B)" as UserB
participant "Next.js" as Client
participant "ChemistryV1Controller" as Controller
participant "ChemistryService" as Chemistry
participant "ChemistryReportProcessor\n(@Async)" as Processor
participant "ChemistryCacheService" as CacheService
participant "ChemistryTxHelper\n(REQUIRES_NEW)" as TxHelper
participant "AnthropicLlmClient" as Llm
participant "ChemistryEventPublisher" as Publisher
participant "ChemistryEventSubscriber" as Subscriber
participant "SseService" as Sse
participant "NotificationService" as Notify
database "MySQL" as DB
database "Redis Pub/Sub" as Redis

== SSE 연결 수립 ==

UserA -> Client : 페이지 진입
Client -> Sse : GET /notifications/stream
note right of Sse
  SseEmitter 생성 후
  Map<userId, SseEmitter>에 보관
  Last-Event-ID 기반 재전송 지원
end note
Sse --> Client : SSE 연결 유지 (text/event-stream)

== 케미 보고서 발행 요청 (발행자 A) ==

UserA -> Client : 동료 목록에서 B 선택\n'케미 보고서 발행' 클릭
Client -> Controller : POST /chemistry-reports\n{ partnerId: B }
activate Controller

Controller -> Chemistry : issue(requesterId: A, partnerId: B)
activate Chemistry

Chemistry -> DB : existsByPair(A, B) — 동료 관계 검증
DB --> Chemistry : true

Chemistry -> DB : findLatestBuckets(A) — 버킷 조회
DB --> Chemistry : A 버킷값 (rd, ri, rs, rc)

Chemistry -> DB : findLatestBuckets(B) — 버킷 조회
DB --> Chemistry : B 버킷값 (pd, pi, ps, pc)

alt A 또는 B의 자기 평정 결과 없음
  Chemistry --> Controller : BusinessException(NO_RESULT)
  Controller --> Client : 400 NO_RESULT
  Client --> UserA : 검사 결과 없음 안내
else 두 사람 모두 결과 있음

  Chemistry -> DB : deduct(A) — 코인 차감
  note right of DB
    UPDATE users SET coins = coins - 1
    INSERT coin_transactions (amount=-1)
  end note
  DB --> Chemistry : 차감 완료

  Chemistry -> DB : INSERT chemistry_reports\n(requesterId=A, partnerId=B,\nstatus=GENERATING, cacheId 세팅)
  DB --> Chemistry : reportId

  Chemistry -> Chemistry : publishEvent(\n  ChemistryReportIssuedEvent\n)
  note right of Chemistry
    @TransactionalEventListener(AFTER_COMMIT)
    트랜잭션 커밋 완료 후 이벤트 발행 보장
    커밋 전 @Async 트리거 문제 원천 차단
  end note

  Chemistry --> Controller : void
  deactivate Chemistry

  Controller --> Client : 202 Accepted
  deactivate Controller
  Client --> UserA : "보고서 생성 중..." 안내

  == 비동기 처리 — 발행자 경로 (트랜잭션 커밋 후 별도 스레드) ==

  activate Processor
  note right of Processor
    @Async 별도 스레드
    @Retryable(maxAttempts=3, backoff=2s×2)
  end note

  Processor -> TxHelper : acquireLockAndDecideRole(\n  cacheId, ttlDays,\n  onSubscriber: registerWaiter()\n)
  activate TxHelper
  note right of TxHelper
    @Transactional(REQUIRES_NEW)
    별도 빈으로 분리 — self-invocation 방지
  end note

  TxHelper -> DB : SELECT FOR UPDATE\nWHERE chemistry_cache.id = cacheId
  DB --> TxHelper : status = NULL (미생성)

  TxHelper -> DB : UPDATE chemistry_cache\nSET status = 'GENERATING'
  TxHelper --> Processor : COMMIT (락 즉시 해제), NULL 반환
  deactivate TxHelper

  Processor -> Llm : complete(prompt)
  activate Llm
  note right of Llm
    섹션 구성:
    1. 두 사람의 성향 요약
    2. 협업 시너지
    3. 갈등 포인트
    4. 소통 방식 차이
    5. 서로에게 맞는 역할
    6. 협업 팁
  end note
  Llm --> Processor : Markdown 보고서
  deactivate Llm

  Processor -> TxHelper : saveCompletedCache(cacheId, report)
  activate TxHelper
  TxHelper -> DB : SELECT FOR UPDATE\nWHERE chemistry_cache.id = cacheId
  TxHelper -> DB : UPDATE chemistry_cache\nSET status='READY', report=?, created_at=NOW()
  TxHelper --> Processor : COMMIT (락 해제)
  note right of TxHelper
    READY 커밋 선행 보장
    이후 신규 요청은 READY를 보고 즉시 반환
  end note
  deactivate TxHelper

  Processor -> Publisher : publishReady(cacheId)
  Publisher -> Redis : PUBLISH chemistry:{버킷 조합} "READY"

  Processor -> TxHelper : completeReport(reportId_A, cacheId)
  activate TxHelper
  TxHelper -> DB : UPDATE chemistry_reports\nSET status='READY'\nWHERE id = reportId_A
  TxHelper --> Processor : COMMIT
  deactivate TxHelper

  Processor -> Notify : sendChemistryNotification(B, report, A)
  Notify -> DB : INSERT chemistry_notifications\n(userId=B, referenceId=reportId_A)

  == Redis Pub/Sub 수신 — 모든 인스턴스 브로드캐스트 ==

  Redis --> Subscriber : onMessage("READY")
  activate Subscriber

  Subscriber -> CacheService : releaseWaiters(cacheId)
  note right of CacheService
    waitingMap에서 cacheId 키 제거
    각 WaitingEntry.latch.countDown()
    → 구독자 스레드 latch.await() 즉시 반환
  end note
  CacheService --> Subscriber : List<WaitingEntry> (userId, reportId)

  Subscriber -> Sse : pushChemistryReady(userId_A, reportId_A)
  Sse --> Client : SSE 이벤트\nevent: CHEMISTRY_REPORT\ndata: { reportId, message: "보고서가 발행됐어요." }
  Client --> UserA : 토스트 알림 + 보고서 카드 갱신

  alt B가 SSE 연결 중
    Subscriber -> Sse : pushChemistryReady(userId_B, reportId_B)
    Sse --> UserB : SSE 이벤트 전송
  end

  deactivate Subscriber
  deactivate Processor

end

== 동일 버킷 조합 동시 요청 — 구독자 경로 (회원 C) ==

UserC -> Controller : POST /chemistry-reports\n{ partnerId: B }
note right of Controller
  C의 버킷값 = A와 동일
  → 동일 cacheId
end note

Controller -> Chemistry : issue(requesterId: C, partnerId: B)
activate Chemistry
Chemistry -> DB : INSERT chemistry_reports\n(requesterId=C, partnerId=B,\nstatus=GENERATING, cacheId 세팅)
Chemistry -> Chemistry : publishEvent(ChemistryReportIssuedEvent)
Chemistry --> Controller : void
deactivate Chemistry
Controller --> Client : 202 Accepted

activate Processor
Processor -> TxHelper : acquireLockAndDecideRole(\n  cacheId, ttlDays,\n  onSubscriber: registerWaiter(C, reportId_C)\n)
activate TxHelper
TxHelper -> DB : SELECT FOR UPDATE
DB --> TxHelper : status = GENERATING

TxHelper -> CacheService : registerWaiter(cacheId, userId_C, reportId_C)
note right of CacheService
  waitingMap.computeIfAbsent(cacheId, CopyOnWriteArrayList::new)
           .add(WaitingEntry(userId_C, reportId_C, latch))
  CopyOnWriteArrayList — 다중 구독자 동시 add 안전
  락 트랜잭션 내 등록 — releaseWaiters 경쟁 원천 차단
end note

TxHelper --> Processor : COMMIT (락 해제), GENERATING 반환
deactivate TxHelper

Processor -> Processor : latch.await() 블로킹
note right of Processor
  park() — CPU 소비 없음
  countDown() 선행 시에도 즉시 반환 (타이밍 안전)
end note

note right of Redis
  발행자가 publishReady() 호출
  → Subscriber.onMessage() 수신
  → releaseWaiters() → latch.countDown()
  → 구독자 latch.await() 즉시 반환
end note

Processor -> TxHelper : completeReport(reportId_C, cacheId)
activate TxHelper
TxHelper -> DB : UPDATE chemistry_reports\nSET status='READY'\nWHERE id = reportId_C
TxHelper --> Processor : COMMIT
deactivate TxHelper

deactivate Processor

== 실패 처리 (@Recover) ==

note over Processor
  @Retryable 3회 소진 시 @Recover 실행
  chemistry_reports.status = ERROR
  TODO: 코인 환불
  구독자에게 pushChemistryError() SSE 전송
end note

@enduml